I can`t speak for any that went, people hide their fears and anguish in different ways. people `wannabe` for different reasons. Some have heroes, some of those heroes were fathers. Others are just sad. The ones who scare me are the psycho-gun- nutters. <br><br>
At least you can walk the streets in yur uniform, proud of who you are and what you do/did.<br>
We have to hide in civilian clothes and take care not to tell the wrong person who we are with, lest the IRA stick a bomb in your car or under the bus.     <br>
